All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class GAGenerationTreePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

A GAGenerationTreePanel object allows for a hierarchical (tree) view of the GAIndividual class to be constructed.

GAGenerationTreePanel is one interpretation of the Model-View-Controller pattern to be used in conjunction with GAApplication.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Pat Burke, Ryan Dixon, Jake Good, Jayapal Prabakaran
